1.This api returns the informations about a specific language like where it was originated and which state and 
what is it capital and currency symbols details.
https://restcountries.com/v3.1/lang/tamil

2.This api returns when we enter a capital of any country it shows the region and sub-region of the country
and how much population it has? and it's area and the neighbouring countries.
https://restcountries.com/v2/capital/delhi

3.This api returns the weather details daily for any location.
https://www.weatherapi.com

